OL,3,CPolice officer charged with causing
OL,4,Cwoman's death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FA police driver who crashed into a
OL,7,Fwoman's car while pursuing a suspected
OL,8,Fstolen vehicle has been charged with
OL,9,Fcausing her death by dangerous driving.
OL,11,FThe unmarked police car being driven
OL,12,Fby the officer was pursuing an Audi A3
OL,13,Fthat was suspected to have been stolen
OL,14,Fwhen the police car crashed into a
OL,15,FPeugeot 108 in Oldham, Greater
OL,16,FManchester.
OL,18,FThe Peugeot's driver, 53-year-old
OL,19,FHeather Smedley, died at the scene, at
OL,20,Fthe junction of Oldham Road and Otmoor
OL,21,FWay on 23 December 2022.
