OL,3,CPolice officer charged with causing
OL,4,Cwoman's death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FPC Mark Burrows has been charged with
OL,7,Fcausing her death by dangerous driving
OL,8,Ffollowing an investigation by the
OL,9,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,10,F(IOPC).
OL,12,FThe watchdog said the 45-year-old
OL,13,Fofficer, who serves with Greater
OL,14,FManchester Police, is due to appear at
OL,15,FWarrington Magistrates' Court on
OL,16,FTuesday.
OL,18,FThe IOPC said its investigation, which
OL,19,Fbegan following a referral from the
OL,20,Fforce in December 2022, ended in
OL,21,FOctober 2023.
