OL,6,FIt said a file of evidence was sent to
OL,7,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,8,Ffor consideration of any potential
OL,9,Fcriminal offence, and the CPS
OL,10,Fauthorised the charge in February 2025.
OL,12,FThe collision happened shortly after
OL,13,F10am and mother-of-three Mrs Smedley
OL,14,Fwas treated at the scene for her
OL,15,Finjuries but died.
OL,17,FAfter her death, Mrs Smedley's family
OL,18,Fpaid tribute, in a statement released
OL,19,Fby Greater Manchester Police, to "the
OL,20,Fmost kind, gentle, beautiful soul
OL,21,Finside and out".
